          "http": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": "https://api.factset.com/wealth/v3/news/article/searchByText",
            "body": {
              "type": "json",
              "data": "{}"
            }
          },
          "docs": "Search for news articles using a fulltext search. All specified criteria need to be fulfilled for an article to match. Each criterion is handled according to its selectionType; \"include\" requires the criterion to evaluate to true, \"exclude\" requires the criterion to evaluate to false. A criterion is fulfilled when at least one of its values is found."
